{"tid":1167060,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"我依加先知盧斯達感情生活咁悲慘","createTime":"2019-05-22T23:32:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-23T20:34:54.000Z","uid":225846,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"f7af45902654062b8ce76f1e2e4b2d179e841043","tid":1167060,"uid":225846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T23:32:44.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: green;\">前度女友Kelly<br />\n<br />\n盧斯達前度女友為任職空姐Kelly，於雨傘革命時曾多度於社交網站發帖斥責香港警察，更指自己不會接受他們「溝」。但在2017年3月，Kelly卻在社交網站發帖，高調指自己已是一名香港警察的女友。當時清黨進行得火熱，盧斯達廣被敵對陣營恥笑。[4]<br />\n<br />\n2018年7月，「香港民族黨」的陳浩天拖女在台北街頭出現，有網民發現那位女子疑似是Kelly。Kelly亦適時於個人Instagram張貼酒店床上自拍照，照片位置顯示是「台北」。她說：「穿自己喜歡的衣服，和不累的人相處，和喜歡的一切待在一起，過想過的一百種生活。」《大公報》刊登兩人照片後，Kelly迅速刪帖刪相，並把帳戶設定為私密，眾人始知「不累的人」原來是指陳浩天。敵對陣營趁機紛紛挖苦，笑指「腎弟、浩天慘成『襟兄弟』，Kelly恐成最大贏家」、「天琦無得食」。[5]<br />\n<br />\n而對於前度的感情變化，盧斯達一直以不作回應的態度面對，任由笑罵。</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/u1KaMZ1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fu1KaMZ1.jpg&h=f4691347&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Hx1kpMH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHx1kpMH.jpg&h=183c2171&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YuqAX6J.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYuqAX6J.jpg&h=9ca4e5e7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e8f7d3e7dba3f82d04314c3e15d0dcfdd920063","tid":1167060,"uid":189911,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T23:35:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/r4oKRtb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fr4oKRtb.jpg&h=b4b04a31&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8685eb5772e26026722c3e79fb8242c5aa517d4f","tid":1167060,"uid":225846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4e8f7d3e7